### Wayle Configuration - Systray Module

## Systray Module Configuration

settings-modules-systray-icon-scale = Icon Scale
    .description = Scale multiplier for tray item icons

settings-modules-systray-item-gap = Item Gap
    .description = Gap between tray items

settings-modules-systray-internal-padding = End Padding
    .description = Padding at container ends (left/right for horizontal, top/bottom for vertical)

settings-modules-systray-blacklist = Blacklist
    .description = Glob patterns for tray items to hide

settings-modules-systray-overrides = Overrides
    .description = Custom icon and color overrides for tray items

settings-modules-systray-border-show = Show Border
    .description = Display border around container

settings-modules-systray-border-color = Border Color
    .description = Border color token

settings-modules-systray-button-bg-color = Button Background
    .description = Container background color

## Tray Item Override Configuration

settings-modules-systray-overrides-name = Pattern
    .description = Glob pattern to match against item ID or title

settings-modules-systray-overrides-icon = Icon
    .description = Custom icon name (symbolic icon)

settings-modules-systray-overrides-color = Color
    .description = Custom icon color
